dct_title_s: Map of the golden northwest : showing location of the great wheat growing region of North Dakota, in the vallies of the Sheyenne, James and Red Rivers
dct_description_sm: Text on verso, The "golden northwest," , surrounded by advertisements. Shows routes of railroads.
